            "title": "聯儲會理事沃勒認為政策仍具限制性 需要進一步降息",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"聯儲會理事沃勒認為政策仍具限制性 需要進一步降息\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/dN0WCNAwnAqQKxfnpZiBAA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-11/307692a0-c94c-11f0-bffd-87ea1d97161b\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">聯儲會理事沃勒認為政策仍具限制性 需要進一步降息</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
